{{Use Australian English|date=November 2016}}
{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2014}}
Dr '''Bernard Whimpress''' is an [[Australian historian]], most active in the area of [[sports history]]. A former sports magazine journalist and photographer, he has written, co-written and edited 37 books, mainly on cricket.
<ref name=curator>{{cite web|url=http://www.harpercollins.com.au/authors/50027482/Bernard_Whimpress/index.aspx |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-01-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111128101108/http://harpercollins.com.au/authors/50027482/Bernard_Whimpress/index.aspx |archivedate=28 November 2011 |df=dmy }}</ref><ref>http://www.cricketworld.com/books/article/?aid=20855</ref>

