'''Giovanni Luca Barberi''' (1452–1520) was an [[Italy|Italian]] [[historian]], lawyer and notary. He was born and lived in [[Sicily]] all of his life.

His writing was particularly important in compiling  the list of [[feudal]] and [[Nobility|noble]] titles in [[Sicily|Sicilian]] [[history]].

